---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Use — nosend.io"
  description="Terms of use for nosend.io. This browser-based image compression tool is provided free of charge, as-is, with no warranty and no liability."
>
  <Header />
  <main class="flex-1 max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-2">Terms of Use</h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-400 mb-10">Last updated: May 2026</p>

    <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none space-y-8 text-slate-600">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Use at your own risk</h2>
        <p>nosend.io is provided free of charge, as-is, with no guarantees of any kind. By using this site you accept that you are solely responsible for any outcome, including but not limited to data loss, file corruption, or any other damage arising from your use of the tools provided.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">No warranty</h2>
        <p>This service is provided "as is" and "as available" without warranty of any kind, express or implied. We make no guarantees that the tools will work correctly, produce accurate results, or be available at any given time.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Limitation of liability</h2>
        <p>To the fullest extent permitted by law, nosend.io and its operators shall not be liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising from your use of this site or the tools provided, even if advised of the possibility of such damages.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Your files</h2>
        <p>All file processing happens locally in your browser. We have no access to your files and accept no responsibility for their contents or condition before or after processing.</p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-800 mb-2">Changes to these terms</h2>
        <p>We may update these terms at any time. Continued use of the site after changes are posted constitutes acceptance of the updated terms.</p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Layout>
